Source: dbic++
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Bharanee Rathna <deepfryed@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.4.0), libpcre3-dev, uuid-dev, libmysqlclient-dev, libpq-dev, db2exc, libevent-dev, cdbs, cmake
Standards-Version: 3.8.4

Package: dbic++-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libpcre3-dev, uuid-dev, libevent-dev
Description: C++ Database Interface (development)
 dbic++ offers a simple DBI style database API. It currently supports MySQL >= 5.1,
 PostgreSQL >= 8.0 and DB2 Express-C >= 9.7.2. Support for SQLite3 is planned.
 .
 This package contains files used for development with dbic++.

Package: dbic++-pg
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, libpq-dev
Description: C++ Database Interface (library)
 dbic++ offers a simple DBI style database API. It currently supports MySQL >= 5.1,
 PostgreSQL >= 8.0 and DB2 Express-C >= 9.7.2. Support for SQLite3 is planned.
 .
 This package contains driver for PostgreSQL.

